headline: Tesla, Netflix set to report earnings as US-China trade fight turns 'unsustainable': What to watch this week
summary: As investors enters shutdown week three, a US-China trade war, credit gesticulation, and an incoming oil glut are weighing on the market.

headline: Freeport-McMoRan (FCX) Valuation: Is There Opportunity After Recent Share Price Pullback?
summary: Freeport-McMoRan (FCX) shares edged lower this week, easing around 1% over the past day and down 9% for the month. Investors seem to be weighing recent price shifts against the company’s longer-term performance. See our latest analysis for Freeport-McMoRan. Despite the recent dip, Freeport-McMoRan’s share price is still up nearly 9% so far this year. However, the 1-year total shareholder return has slid to negative territory. Momentum has cooled lately as investors weigh growth prospects...
